4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners, requiring no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students will learn Python, SQL, and various statistics while working on predictive models using tools like Pandas and Numpy. The course includes 3 classes weekly, with a maximum class size of 12. Participants will engage in real-life projects and master the A.I. project lifecycle, ensuring data privacy and security. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. The classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop